        <div class="sect-title-wrapper">
          <h2 class="sect-title">Hand Drawn Tech</h2>
          <div class="underline"></div>
        </div>

      
  
      <div class="text-wrapper">    
        
        
          <p>Encouraged by positive client feedback, Scott was convinced there was a market for his whimsical low-tech creations. So, in June 2022 he launched <b>Hand Drawn Tech</b>, a place to licence his inventive illustrations or to commission new ones.</p>
        

        
        

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         

        
         


         

         

